      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/euro-parity-with-dollar-is-the-big-new-call-by-currency-analysts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国大选之后，货币策略师们纷纷推翻对欧元的预测，并提出了新的预测：欧元将跌至与美元平价。]]></description>
